        <mxCell id="8AAtuygDwCT9gFwMfxLB-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontSize=32;" value="&lt;div&gt;Design a hotstar like application with the following requirements:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1.User Login Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. Subscribe Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. Movie/TV show Search Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. Movie/TV show Play Service&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Optimise the application using using CDC Pipeline, Highlight where proxy Design Pattern Can be used&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Use HLS and Dash for a specific live static content playing along with manifest file&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
